docs.lead_paragraph: A happy event for Costa Rica and for the progress of democracy in Latin America has just been celebrated in the charming and beautiful little Central American country. Jose Figueres ("Don Pepe" is what he must be called) was yesterday inaugurated President of a country which is less well known than that other little gem to the south -- Uruguay -- but which ranks with her in the virtues of democracy.
